citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 2:43 pm on
19-Dec-18.
Telephone contact was made with the licensee who was working and unable to leave. The licensee stated she will
text me her new schedule after the holiday on the 25th.
